title: Stuck on transfer
body: Bought a region transfer from na to oce 2 days ago, but when i try logging on from na client it says my account is in the process of transferring and when i try logging onto oce client it says incorrect login, ign: ceiiu

replies.body:
Hi

That does sound pretty strange - hopefully it can be sorted out quickly.  If you haven't yet, your best bet will be to send in a ticket on the [Support](https://support.riotgames.com) site, who should be able to sort it out for you.

Cheers
Mindstar
